Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積在身上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為已經等了整整兩小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為才兩點左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算才兩點 也遲到一小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 還記得我的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是要問你 還記得我的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家是女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 真的要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做著一個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個每天都做的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有盡頭的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被染成紅色的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛要遮蓋夕陽的天空的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個正在哭泣的孩童
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少想拭去他流出的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 卻聯手也舉不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水劃過臉頰 滲入雪中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能靜靜地看著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好無助 好悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這言語是誰說的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢漸漸被染成其他顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 約定好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服 制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的已經沒有時間了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服 制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的就在吵什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上要好好說一聲「早上好」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祐一 知道我的制服在哪兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是秋子阿姨拿去洗了嗎 我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的設計啊 這套制服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了哦 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還有點濕濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到被爐裏馬上就會幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做的話 會變得皺巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是冬季生活的常識哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要這樣的生活常識呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不還是寒假中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但我還有社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還是部長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的確也有說過練習什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 田徑部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪是田徑部的部長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是濕濕的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快一些可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這個時間了 現在去還來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出一百米七秒跑完的速度就來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這刷新世界紀錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨 這口鍋是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我走了咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過會兒能不能帶我參觀一下這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我完全沒有問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點小事沒什麼 我走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心汽車哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累吧 累了的話休息一下也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男孩子在還真是幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我母親的妹妹 水瀨秋子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名雪的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經到那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的時候 我經常來這座城市遊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和名雪以及秋子阿姨 則是闊別七年後的再會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼祐一 我來帶你參觀這個城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 你還是一點都沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是我一點都沒成長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地讓你陪著真抱歉了 才剛剛回到家的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕快適應這個城市才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為祐一以後要一直生活在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道會不會一直生活在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少高中畢業前會一直生活在這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（1832 拖車到黑石署報到）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防滑砂）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的學校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近以前是麥田吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這邊是新校舍 那邊是舊校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還在假期 學生還真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有補習和社團等等各種活動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從明天開始我也將成為這裏的學生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你好久了 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在給小狗餵食了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在撫摸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏是醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太想和那地方扯上關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一很怕去醫院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人會喜歡醫院的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,75)\fs57}冷嗎 栞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,75)\fs57}還好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近還真是變得熱鬧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我常常在對面的商店街買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香裏 北川君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:10:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同班同學 香裏可是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見呢 水瀨也在約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫也在 我們只不過是偶然遇到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你別讓偶然遇到的傢伙拿這麼多東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是相澤祐一 是我的表哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美阪香裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我香裏就行了 相澤君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責給她提行李的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰是提行李的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川君 幫我拿一下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是提行李的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是的 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 作為友好的表示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我買的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說這麼小氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說在前面 不要對香裏出手 香裏是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是同班同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 明天學校見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我做男朋友候補吧 香裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香裏小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆和我坐得很近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個山丘一點都沒變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 只是過去的事情記不太清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然感覺發生過很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大多忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連是不是真的喜歡這個城市也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因為當時還小 現在並沒有懷念之類的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的許多事情一定會慢慢想起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也希望祐一能夠喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來吧～小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來 過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了 會被咬的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是那麼喜歡動物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來～過來～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是野生的狐狸吧 哪會那麼容易親近人類
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 這個山丘上的狐狸是很特別的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有個古老的傳說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼傳說？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該去買晚飯的材料了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏等你好了 進去好像會迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為有你在才擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你在這裏等著 不可以走開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我站在這裏一動不動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起以前也有過相似的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前 我也看過這樣的景色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快閃開 快閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕 快閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為速度太快了沒能避開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶跑得才沒那麼快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請別謙虛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 有話等會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裏就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼安不安全的 我連發生了什麼都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶正被人追呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被發現和偶在一起 你也會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經決定要點的菜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會兒再點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙在追你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你那個紙袋有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完 完全沒有一點關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是個很善良的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不可貌相哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他穿著圍裙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是烤鯛魚燒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼鯛魚燒大叔要來追你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個賣鯛魚燒的地方偶很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點了很多的時候都還很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想付錢的時候 卻發現錢包不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在想該怎麼辦的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊來了一隻想要偷吃鯛魚燒的小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔一副兇相畢露的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是偶也嚇了一跳 然後就逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說的話 完全是你單方面的錯咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕 還有別的原因嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來話長了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緣由極其複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子實在太餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼聽都是你的不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶明天會好好地去付錢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢我來付 現在馬上去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 能得到原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然鯛魚燒還是剛燒好的最美味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶才不在乎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我監督你把剩下的全吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:16:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕 別學人家的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你從剛才開始就一直在用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕 才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背後的翅膀是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有翅膀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你背後的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕 看不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭時身體別動就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 有翅膀耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點察覺到了 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個怪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕 才沒有這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就此告別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好還錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶叫月宮亞由 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相澤祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是還能見面就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然咯 你這麼說話小心不還你錢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下次再見了 約定好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉 我從剛才就一直在道歉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等了你半個鐘頭的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 昨天我也遲到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搬家的行李都送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來光靠今天是收拾不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先找個鬧鐘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 把我的借你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幾個好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個就夠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡哪個隨便挑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有收集的興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有這回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一的話 推薦這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要說「晚安」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新城市的新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的冬季的一天慢慢過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在半夢半醒之際 一個少女的身影浮現在腦海裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不清楚那是誰的情況下 我睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話太陽要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽讓我幫忙去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一說好幫拿東西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太冷了 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就要紮千針
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在增量期間要紮千五百針
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一也進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏等你好了 進去好像會迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為有你在才擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了 你在這裏等著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚咕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 為什麼要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫相澤祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓也是亞由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被欺負了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先離開這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 亞由亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:21:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是亞由亞由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼果醬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相澤祐一 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的成同班了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒還要去道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.23,0:24:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 剛才好像有走過這條路？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像以前一樣拉鉤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.81,0:24:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.35,0:24:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
